@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_moeuaq(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = (wp.abs((v2 + 0.00 - v2 + 0.83)) - ((v0 + 0.08 + tmp + 0.44) * 0.55))
    tmp = (v2 * 0.21)
    v1 = (tmp * wp.exp((tmp + 0.33 - v0 + 0.89)))
    v1 = (((tmp + 0.46 + tmp + 0.96) / (v0 + 0.91 - v1 + 0.47)) * (wp.exp(v2 + 0.43) + tmp))
    tmp = v1
    data[tid] = v0
